text:
Hi Akshat, the government guidelines tell very clearly that if you can only make investment in private listed companies if and only if you are an accredited investor. 
For being an accredited investor, you should have a proper certification where you have to prove that your net worth is more than 2.5crores without your primary residence.

So not sure if this is the right way to invest into startups.
